  - LanguageType: 1
    Title: HORSE RACE
    ClassicText: BASIC
    SettingText: SETTING
    EventText: EVENT
    EventDescription: 
    RoleTitle: RULE
    RoleText: "- Each one roll the dice to get moving point, one fills all the higher
      positions on the stable first is the winner.\r\n - 1 point and 6 point can
      continue to roll dice.\r\n - Piece at home need 1 or 6 point to go on board
      (at the arrow mark).\r\n - Piece move as moving point, will be blocked when
      there's another piece on moving route.\r\n - If other's piece stand on target
      position, move and kick other's piece back home.\r\n - If no move available,
      skip turn.\r\n - When get to stable the first time, move as moving point, pieces
      do block each other.\r\n - When on stable, only moving each step by get move
      point as the number marked."
    YourTurnText: Your turn!
    WinText: WIN !!
